## Community Playbook Content
## What is a language

about-playbook-what-is-language = Common Voice irratti qooqa jechuun maali dha?
about-playbook-what-is-language-content-1 = waa'ee qooqaa yaaduuf karaaleen hedduun jiru. Kaayyoo moodeelota beekumsa sagalee (speech recognition) tiif, Afaan Waloo’n “wal hubannaa waliigalaa” irratti xiyyeeffata. Kana jechuunis, “namoonni qooqa kana dubbatan yoo yaalan, wal hubachuu ni danda’uu?” jechuun of gaafata.
about-playbook-what-is-language-content-2 = Moodeelonni sagalee akka caalaatti fooyya’anii hojjetaniif, sagalee fi aksentoota garaagaraa hubachuun barbaachisaadha. Kanaafuu, kuusaan odeeffannoo sagalee (voice dataset) namoota hedduu fi garaagarummaa hawaasaa bal’aa bakka bu’uu qaba.
about-playbook-what-is-language-content-3 = Qooqni tokko tokko seera-jecha (grammar), fayyadama jechootaa fi sagaleedhaan garaagarummaa guddaa qabaachuu danda’a. Sababa kanaaf, bara 2022tti <ctaLink>“garaagarummaa qooqaa (variants)”</ctaLink> jedhaman beeksifne. Kun hawaasota akka qooqa isaaniitti kuusaa odeeffannoo guddaa keessatti addaan baafatan carraa ni kenna.

## How do I add a language

about-playbook-how-add-language = Qooqa akkamiin ida'a?
about-playbook-how-add-language-content-1 =
    Jalqaba, afaan kee <languageLink>dursee jiraachuu</languageLink> isaa ilaali. Yoo hin jirre, <languageRequestLink>waa'ee afaan kee dabaluuf</languageRequestLink> gaafachuu dandeessa.
    Gulantaan lama jiru: Marsariitii hiikuu fi himoota walitti qabuu.
about-playbook-how-add-language-translating-heading = Marsariitii hiikuu
about-playbook-how-add-language-translating-content-1 = <translateVideoLink>Pontoon akkamitti fayyadamu akka dandeessu gorsa keenya ilaali.</translateVideoLink>
about-playbook-how-add-language-translating-content-2 =
    Hiikkaaf qodaa Mozilla <pontoonLink>Pontoon</pontoonLink> fayyadamna. Pontoon afaanota hedduu qaba, garuu yoo afaan kee hin jirre, afaan kee <pontoonRequestLink>dabaluuf gaafachuu</pontoonRequestLink> dandeessa.
    Achii booddee, afaan sun projektii Common Voice irratti akka argamu gochuuf, <githubRepoLink>afaan haaraa GitHub</githubRepoLink> irratti gaafadhu. Marsariitii hiikkaa irraa <localizationFragment>odeeffannoo dabalataa ilaali.</localizationFragment>
about-playbook-how-add-language-collecting-sentences-heading = Himoota walitti qabuu
about-playbook-how-add-language-collecting-sentences-content-1 = <sentenceCollectorVideo>Akkamitti hima walitti qabu akka dandeessu gorsa keenya ilaali</sentenceCollectorVideo>
about-playbook-how-add-language-collecting-sentences-content-2 =
    <sentenceCollectorLinkAdd>Himoota xiqqoo dabalu</sentenceCollectorLinkAdd>, 
    yookaan <bulkImportDocsLink>bu’uura GitHub fayyadamuun himoota baay’ee galchuu</bulkImportDocsLink> dandeessa. 
    Yaadadhu, himoonni <licenseLink>CC0 (yookaan public domain)</licenseLink> ta’uu qabu, yookaan ati mataa keetiin barreessuu dandeessa.
about-playbook-how-add-language-collecting-sentences-content-3 = <sentenceCollectorFragment>Himoota walitti qabuu irratti odeeffannoo dabalataa ilaali</sentenceCollectorFragment>.

## How does localization work

about-playbook-how-localize = Marsariitii naannootti jijjiiruun akkamiin hojjetaa?
about-playbook-how-localize-content-1 = Hiikkaan marsariitii Common Voice <strong>Pontoon</strong> irratti ni hojjetama.
about-playbook-how-localize-content-2 = <pontoonAccountLink>Akkaawontii uumii</pontoonAccountLink> yoo hin qabaanne. Achii booddee, afaan kee <strong>(‘Team’)</strong> filadhu, booda projektii <pontoonCvLink>Common Voice</pontoonCvLink> filadhu. Faayiloonni hiikamuuf jiru ni mul’atu. Faayila tokko cuqaasi, achii immoo jechoota Afaan Ingilizii fi sanduuqa hiikkaa agarsiisa.
about-playbook-how-localize-content-3 = Hiikkaan Afaan Ingilizii irraa ta’a, garuu <strong>Yaada</strong> afaanota biroo arguu dandeessa. Mallattoo <strong>Profile</strong> cuqaasi, booda <strong>Settings</strong> link filadhu akkasumas afaanota ati dubbistu dabali. Gadi harka mirgaa irratti tarree hiikkaa <strong>Locales</strong> jedhamu ni argatta. Hiikkaaleen guyyaa tokko booda marsariitii irratti mul’atu.
about-playbook-how-localize-content-4 = Marsariitiin yeroo %75 ga'u gadlakkifamuuf qophii xumura.
about-playbook-how-localize-content-5 = Gorsa argachuuf viidiyoo keenya ilaali.

## How to add sentences

about-playbook-how-add-sentences = Himoota akkamitti daballa?
about-playbook-how-add-sentences-content-1 = Himoota <writePageLink>Fuula Barreessuu</writePageLink> irratti dabali, yookaan himoota <reviewPageLink>Fuula Gamaggamuu</reviewPageLink> irratti gamaggami.
about-playbook-how-add-sentences-content-2 = Himoonni namoota biraa lama waliin gamaggamamanii fudhatamuu qabu akka Common Voice keessa galaniif. Qajeelfamoota afaan kee <languageGuidelinesLink>asitti</languageGuidelinesLink> uumi. Himoonni <licenseLink>public domain</licenseLink> keessaa ta’uu qabu akkasumas jechoota 15 hin caalle ta’anii. Barreessaa barruu tokko gaafachuudhaan <waiverLink>CC0 gochuu</waiverLink> dandeessa, booda nuuf ergi commonvoice@mozilla.com irratti.
about-playbook-how-add-sentences-content-3 = Himoota gabaaboo Wikipedia irraa argachuuf <scraperLink>Sentence extractor</scraperLink> fayyadami.

## How to record quality

about-playbook-how-record-quality = Sagalee qulqullina ol’aanaa qabu akkamitti waraabuu danda’a?
about-playbook-how-record-content-1 = Sagalee kee isa sirriimaan dubbadhu! Akka ati itti dubbattu bareedaa - loqoda sirrii ittiin dubbattu barbaanna, jechoota kee akkasitti, sagalee, kallattii fi jecha sirrii waliin dhaggeeffachuuf.
about-playbook-how-record-content-2 = Waca dudduubaa baayyee balleessi - sagaleen kee sirriitti dhagahamuu qaba.
about-playbook-how-record-content-3 = Himicha sirriitti dubbisi - jechoota itti hin dabaliin, irraa hin hir'isiin.
about-playbook-how-record-content-4 = Sagaleen kee eegaluu dura, platformiin waraabbii sagalee eegalu isaa mirkaneessi, akkasumas xumuramuun yeroo ati fixxe qofa akka ta’e mirkaneessi.
about-playbook-how-record-content-5 = <accuracyLink>Ulaagaa sirrummaaf himoota dabalataa ilaali.</accuracyLink>

## How to grow language

about-playbook-how-grow-language = Afaan tokko Common Voice irratti dagaagsuun akkamitti danda’ama?
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-1 = Namoota garaagaraa Common Voice keessatti qooda fudhachuu danda’an carraa uumuun, daataa-seetii namoota hedduuf tajaajilu akka ta’u mirkaneessa. Horataa fi fakkeenyawwan ati fayyadamuu dandeessu uumneerra!
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-2 = Taateewwan
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-3 = Namoota gumaachaan gargaaruuf sagantaalee geggeessuu dandeessa. Kana gochuun kan ati yaaddu caalaa salphaa dha. Online ta’uun meeshaa videoconferencing fayyadamuun, yookaan bakka naga qabeessa ta’e irratti ammoo nama waliin geggeessuu dandeessa. Fakkeenyawwanii fi horata sagantaalee geggeessuuf <eventTemplate>taateewwan keenya ilaali.<eventTemplate>
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-4 = Miidiyaa hawaasaa
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-5 = Ergaa babal’isuuf marsariitii miidiyaa hawaasaa fayyadamuu dandeessa. Barreessuu fi maxxansoota waa’ee maaliif barbaachisu ibsan qooduu, akkasumas namoota kaayyoo afaanii, sagalee AI, yookaan yaada dogoggoraa tekinoolojii irratti dubbatan waliin qunnamuu. Gorsa dabalataa <campaignLink>sagantaa miidiyaa hawaasaa geggeessuu, akkasumas qooddachuu dandeessu ilaali</campaignLink>.”
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-6 = Hariiroowwanii fi neetworkii
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-7 = Namoota biroo fedhii qaban barbaadi. Yuunivarsiitiiwwan, manneen barnootaa afaanii, gareewwan abukaatummaa, ykn hawaasa saayinsii daataa ta’uu danda’u. Akkamitti gargaaruu akka danda’an fi maaliif akka ta’e ifatti ibsi. <outreachTemplates>Imeelii qunnamtii fakkeenya keenyaa</outreachTemplates> ilaali.
about-playbook-how-grow-language-content-8 = <strong>Uumama argadhu!</strong> Hawaasni afaanii kee addaa dha, kanaafis karaalee muraasa jalqabsiisuun ni danda’ama.

## How to validate

about-playbook-how-validate = Kiliippiin sagalee sirrii ta’uu isaa akkamitti beeka?
about-playbook-how-validate-content-1 = Yoo <strong>dhaggeeffachuu</strong> fi <strong>hubachuu</strong> dandeesse, yeroo baay’ee <strong>mirkaneessuuf</strong> gaarii dha.
about-playbook-how-validate-content-2 = Yoo sagaleen dubbataa kan kee irraa adda ta’ellee, kiliippiilee hin haqiin — kun sirni sagalee namoota hundaaf akka gaariitti hojjetuuf barbaachisaa dha.
about-playbook-how-validate-content-3 = Yoo sagaleessuun <strong>hubachuu hin dandeessisu</strong> jettee yaadde, yookaan <strong>wacni duubbee baay’een</strong> jiraate, yookaan namoonni biroo dubbatan yoo jiraatan, kutaa sana diduu qabda. <accuracyLink>Odeeffannoo dabalataa ulaagaalee sirrii ta’uu keenya</accuracyLink> ilaali.
about-playbook-how-validate-content-4 = Yoo namoonni lama kutaa tokko didan, kuusaa deetaa adda ta’een ni gadhiifama.

## How to access dataset

about-playbook-how-access-dataset = Akkamitti kuusaa deetaa argachuu fi itti fayyadamuu danda’a?
about-playbook-how-access-dataset-content-1 = Gara <datasetsPage>Fuula Tuuta Deetaa</datasetsPage> deemi, gosa fi afaan(ota) barbaadde filadhu, sana booda buufadhu. Faayiloonni <metadataLink>meetaadaataa</metadataLink> qabu, kan akka odeeffannoo dimogiraafii fi deetaa mirkaneessuu. Kuusaa deetaa buufachuuf teessoo imeelii kennuu si barbaachisa.
about-playbook-how-access-dataset-content-2 = Yoo meeshaalee moodeelota beekamtii dubbii (ASR) ijaaruuf barbaadde, hawaasa <discourseLink>Discourse</discourseLink> irratti namoota biroo waliin walqunnamuu dandeessa.

## How are decisions made

about-playbook-how-project-governance = Murtoon pirojektii akkamitti murtaa’a?
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-1 = Sagaleen Waliigalaa tattaaffii walta’iinsaa aktivistoota, ogeeyyii afaanii, saayintistoota deetaa, barsiisota, fi injinaroota sooftiweerii addunyaa irraa walitti fiduudhaani. Pirojektichi kan hoogganamu Mozilla Foundationiitiin.
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-2 = Bulchiinsi keenya utubaawwan armaan gadii irratti hundaa’a:
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-3 = Mateenya, Nageenya, fi Iftoomina.
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-4 = Hirmaannaa Hawaasaa fi Murtee Kennuu.
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-5 = Gatii fi Beekkamtii.
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-6 = Itti Gaafatamummaa Waliinii.
about-playbook-how-project-governance-content-7 = <governanceLink>Waa’ee akkaataa itti bulchinu caalaatti dubbisi</governanceLink>

## How is Common Voice funded

about-playbook-how-funded = Common Voice akkamitti maallaqaan deeggarama?
about-playbook-how-funded-content-1 = Common Voice pirojektii Mozilla Foundation kan US 501(c)(3) ti. Amma pirojektichi guutummaatti <philantropicGrantLink>gargaarsa tola ooltummaa</philantropicGrantLink> fi arjooma namoota addunyaa irraa argamuun deeggarama.
about-playbook-how-funded-content-2 = Kuusaa deetaa walitti fufiinsaan keessummeessuu fi gadhiisuuf, waltajjii fooyyessuuf, akkasumas <africaMradiLink>sagantaalee hawaasaa </africaMradiLink> hojiirra oolchuuf maallaqa guddaa baasisa.
about-playbook-how-funded-content-3 = Yoo ati yookaan dhaabbanni kee pirojekticha deeggaruu barbaadde, <donateLink>arjooma gochuu</donateLink> yookaan garee walta’iinsa keenyaa <emailFragment>commonvoice@mozilla.com</emailFragment> qunnamuu dandeessa.
